create a trigger to validate UPDATE operation on a table if new salary is less than to old salary?
SQL> CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER TRUPDATE
  2  BEFORE UPDATE ON EMPLOYEE
  3  FOR EACH ROW
  4  BEGIN
  5  IF :NEW.SAL<:OLD.SAL THEN
  6  RAISE_APPLICATION_ERROR(-20456,'NEW SALARY NOT BE LESS THAN TO OLD SALARY');
  7  END IF;
  8  END;
  9  /

TESTING:
========
SQL> UPDATE EMPLOYEE SET SAL=2500 WHERE SAL=3000; // Not allowed
SQL> UPDATE EMPLOYEE SET SAL=6500 WHERE SAL=3000; // Allowed
